Hi Ron.  There&#39;s plenty of room for long clips if people would change their software 
settings, as well as post in MP3 format rather than WAV. 

Hi LK.  I would add, &#39;disclose when you have edited&#39;, so others aren&#39;t mislead by your 
results.

Margaret

